gmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1ead90b7b61dba2e19d5ed0ed0e43bdb75a08c","tid":122911,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由5D's開始無睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺已經唔係以前個回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5Ds 神作黎</blockquote><br />\n5Ds 頭26集神作嚟</blockquote><br />\n前面覺得幾好睇，後半開始唔知發生咩事無再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本來頭26集勁多伏筆<br />\n到之後dark signer 已經開始戇鳩<br />\n屌 個念力佬半集比人秒撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明果條友都夠整多26集 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a31e4b60faa5e2be3e5b6e5981cd97aed1b745f","tid":122911,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:51:48.000Z","msg":"除左第一輯法老王 其他都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161964468dba3b177a8ef9e17c3a26ff4f04ab17","tid":122911,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/erqahA8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FerqahA8.jpg&h=f42c0338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[VJMP Spoilers] Decode Talker &amp; Link Summon revealed!<br />\nFEB 17, 2017by DSUMMONin PRODUCT NEWS<br />\nAfter the long wait, VJump is finally in, and we finally have info on the new gameplay mechanism! It&rsquo;s time for Link Summon!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDecode Talker<br />\nDark Cybers-Type Link / Effect Monster<br />\nLINK 3 2300<br />\n2 or more effect monsters<br />\n(1) This card gains 500 ATK for each monster Linked to it.<br />\n(2) When an opponent&rsquo;s card effect that targets a card you control is activated: You can Tribute 1 of your monsters Linked to this card; negate that activation, and if you do, destroy it.<br />\n<br />\nLook at those distinctive Link Markers! Use these Markers to develop brand new strategies!<br />\nIt goes into your Extra Deck!<br />\n<br />\nThere are 2 ways of Link Summoning!!<br />\n<br />\n&gt;Send Materials to the Grave Equal to the Link Number!<br />\nYou can Link Summon something from your Extra Deck by sending the same number of monsters that meet the material requirements written in the card&rsquo;s effect box, whose total numbers equal to the LINK number, from the field to the Graveyard<br />\n&gt;Decrease Materials by Using Link Monsters<br />\nLink Monsters are treated as the same number of materials as its LINK Number, however to use them you must match the requirements written on the card!<br />\n<br />\nIN THE CASE OF &ldquo;DECODE TALKER&rdquo;<br />\nYou can either<br />\n-Use 3 Effect Monsters<br />\nor<br />\n-Use a [Link 2] Effect monster and 1 Effect Monster<br />\n<br />\nPay Attention to the Direction of the Link Markers!<br />\n<br />\nThe Zones pointed to by each Link Marker and the cards in them will be affected by the Link Monster, and this will create new strategies!<br />\n<br />\nThey have no defense&hellip;!!!<br />\nLink monsters have no defense points and they have the special characteristics of being unable to change their battle positions or turning to defense position by effects."},{"pid":"bbcf971c1573be21c37e9169839f94be26f15b5f","tid":122911,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:07:35.000Z","msg":"連星數都無埋,<br />\n仲以玩過超量,<br />\n不過無得防守表示,<br />\n不過你合得大怪就預左唔會防守表示架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n似乎遊戲個打法遲D係D怪瘋狂送墓到Link9<br />\n但有冇Link12真係會係一個疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba03658b31023fcf88cccbe25918096f27796e3","tid":122911,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/coW0e6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcoW0e6f.jpg&h=9069368e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第6個怪獸區?<br />\n姐係話自己場上只可以有一隻link怪?"},{"pid":"bc033023dd4a7c3ecd481dd59d626dc3c358344c","tid":122911,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"The Monster Zone of old is now called the Main Monster Zone!<br />\nPendulum Zones now<span style=\"color: red;\"> take up the Left Most and Right Most Zones of your Spell &amp; Trap Zones instead</span>! And when they do, those Zones become Pendulum Zones!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0e8d33c1c8bfc08b578edf7632d1c0bc0a2acb","tid":122911,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1a97Bx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1a97Bx.jpg&h=28b98c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThe Zones Pointed at by Link Markers Can be Used to Bring Out Extra Deck Monsters<br />\n<br />\nAlthough<span style=\"color: red;\"> Extra Deck Monsters can only be Summoned to the Extra Monster Zone Normally, if you have a Link Monster in the Extra Monster Zone, the Zones pointed at by their Link Markers can be used to Summon Extra Deck Monsters! </span>So if you get out a Link Summon quickly, you can bring out Fusion, Synchro, and Xyz Monsters in succession. Of course, you can Summon another Link Monster in one of these Zones, so if you play your cards right, you can fill your entire Main Monster Zone with Extra Deck Monsters! The new metagame will require careful consideration of where to place monsters!<br />\n簡單D黎講姐係你以後無得好無賴咁成台Extra deck出黎既大獸.<br />\n一定局你用新既Link怪霸左個extra monster zone先,之後你先可以玩番以前果種召喚方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17218f2a279e80aa479e553505e4a511f99d0f3b","tid":122911,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:35:32.000Z","msg":"Super Quick Q&amp;A for the New Rules!<br />\nQ: If Special Summoned an Extra Deck Monster normally, and it goes to the Graveyard, and I want to Special Summon it with &ldquo;Monster Reborn&rdquo;, which Zone does it go to?<br />\nA: It goes into the Main Monster Zone, not the Extra Monster Zone.<br />\nQ: Can you use &ldquo;Book of Moon&rdquo; on Link Monsters?<br />\nA: <span style=\"color: red;\">Link Monsters cannot be face-down</span>, so you cannot target them with &ldquo;Book of Moon&rdquo;.<br />\nQ: If your opponent&rsquo;s only monster is in their Extra Monster Zone, can you attack them directly?<br />\nA: If there&rsquo;s a monster in the Extra Monster Zone, unless some kind of effect is in play, you would have to attack that monster first.<br />\nQ: Can you destroy 2 Set Spell &amp; Trap Cards in your Left Most and Right Most Spell &amp; Trap Zones with &ldquo;Wavering Eyes&rdquo;?<br />\nA: The Left Most and Right Most Spell &amp; Trap Zones are regular Spell &amp; Trap Zones, and do not become Pendulum Zones unless you activate a Pendulum Card in them, or if a Pendulum Card is placed in them by a card effect. A Set Spell &amp; Trap Card in either of those Zones cannot be destroyed by &ldquo;Wavering Eyes&rdquo;.<br />\n最尾係講一定要開左P召你先可以炸,<br />\n唔可以放魔陷都照炸P區"},{"pid":"4aca741880d11c198b07cf13bd85fe1c737cf2d3","tid":122911,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T13:10:08.000Z","msg":"一齊玩mtg算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13e367807bad841f6cbc0384002c71d77ca93b6","tid":122911,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T14:59:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連星數都無埋,<br />\n仲以玩過超量,<br />\n不過無得防守表示,<br />\n不過你合得大怪就預左唔會防守表示架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n似乎遊戲個打法遲D係D怪瘋狂送墓到Link9<br />\n但有冇Link12真係會係一個疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁究竟係送場上/手卡定卡組d怪去墓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076bd7d3885f08570b404524ecb9bb61bfaa4f66","tid":122911,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:18:16.000Z","msg":"Arcv真係角色同背景都好正<br />\n係劇情推得太on9同動作卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba510c3f58dd698f23545d69da710e5ed33ae76","tid":122911,"uid":34584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"其實主角人設係咪已經冇可能去得番 遊戲  十代  遊星 果type??<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf7a48d734a8a264f7215c2e612adf31b83a51d","tid":122911,"uid":2380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由5D's開始無睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺已經唔係以前個回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5Ds 神作黎</blockquote><br />\n5Ds 頭26集神作嚟</blockquote><br />\n前面覺得幾好睇，後半開始唔知發生咩事無再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去到地縛神篇都仲叫好睇<br />\n<br />\n之後就比紅龍個設定屈住黎作故仔<br />\n<br />\n睇到加速同步果度就頂唔順棄番<br />\n<br />\nbtw 大師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147cb95023508a8f4cace09bc60470361f13b4af","tid":122911,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連星數都無埋,<br />\n仲以玩過超量,<br />\n不過無得防守表示,<br />\n不過你合得大怪就預左唔會防守表示架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n似乎遊戲個打法遲D係D怪瘋狂送墓到Link9<br />\n但有冇Link12真係會係一個疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係要適應下 玩一次先知佢up乜<br />\n<br />\n屌 我d魔術師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd67f79dd9d6fed5b0eda90c4787060ee392401","tid":122911,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T23:30:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g4JwD5qab0E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg4JwD5qab0E&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=5962a40e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g4JwD5qab0E</a><br />\n呢段片最尾講左Link mark既方向先可以召Extra deck既怪,<br />\n同埋佢講左最重要既野係以後點出類天流星龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4182c1ed9436c28e0cd7f50a5e1996f4181fe592","tid":122911,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T23:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連星數都無埋,<br />\n仲以玩過超量,<br />\n不過無得防守表示,<br />\n不過你合得大怪就預左唔會防守表示架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n似乎遊戲個打法遲D係D怪瘋狂送墓到Link9<br />\n但有冇Link12真係會係一個疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁究竟係送場上/手卡定卡組d怪去墓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n場上"},{"pid":"3a1c38d847bcf365728dcabc90309f02c6afdb26","tid":122911,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T05:04:10.000Z","msg":"on9規則<br />\n我副銀河玩撚咩<br />\n<br />\n一round大多數出2隻5星+8星<br />\n5星我出電子龍無限好過<br />\n8星出一隻點企場<br />\n本身已經冇續航 <br />\n如果我要出少隻R8/R5 出一隻link monster真係同讓半臂冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7607c437e40b9cecdc7ff88b07811a35a4a53e9","tid":122911,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T05:20:25.000Z","msg":"btw技抽列車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8b60edfdf50ba9059e2cc6877ce5370f456017","tid":122911,"uid":10162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T05:46:28.000Z","msg":"藍色果張卡有向上箭嘴，即係可以祭對面隻獸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880b75d358c336c852b920626956597df15b959c","tid":122911,"uid":65780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:21:59.000Z","msg":"其實點解每個新系列一定要有新嘅召喚方法？<br />\n第一代有融合 Gx主題都係融合<br />\n點解唔抄冷飯 例如主題係儀式or普通召喚<br />\n同咁主角自從5ds開始主角就好7"},{"pid":"88532da4620ad3527538c49409bbdb237a91001d","tid":122911,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T07:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解每個新系列一定要有新嘅召喚方法？<br />\n第一代有融合 Gx主題都係融合<br />\n點解唔抄冷飯 例如主題係儀式or普通召喚<br />\n同咁主角自從5ds開始主角就好7</blockquote><br />\n不停出新card 等人買"},{"pid":"1af673272e4a93ffb9f22723936394d5bfd3be34","tid":122911,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"唔可以召ex怪，難怪咁多人退坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d3bb95d032dcf3f3a371f1fb73bc42f3de3bc7","tid":122911,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔可以召ex怪，難怪咁多人退坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本來佢地係咁出新規則係阻止遊戲王高速喚既情況<br />\n所以出P召,同時又阻止先攻DRAW一張卡既問題<br />\n點知個P召無改變個情況仲搞到隻GAME召得仲快更加不受控制.<br />\n跟本KONAMI無打算改變隻GAME<br />\n就算佢而家出左LINK怪.<br />\n我相信好快又出D極變態COMBO係咁瘋狂召怪.<br />\n所以無咩影響.<br />\n成個新系統最大輸家係類天流星龍.<br />\n因為佢要額外怪有link mark怪<br />\n而Link mark怪據而家仲未有係左右方向link mark,姐係召唔到唔第三隻同步怪.<br />\n跟本就合唔撚到類天流星龍."},{"pid":"d6e2778ce1f965a5a6b367dc19d27e139ff91ea6","tid":122911,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9規則<br />\n我副銀河玩撚咩<br />\n<br />\n一round大多數出2隻